{
  "id": "69ac2eba95d89b1ac69088a7",
  "title": "健康で非文化的な最低限度の食事",
  "created": 1772891835,
  "updated": 1772895262,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69ac2eba95d89b1ac69088a7",
      "text": "健康で非文化的な最低限度の食事",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772891835,
      "updated": 1772891835
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac321d00000000004fd117",
      "text": " 栄養があるけれど、文化してない食事",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772892702,
      "updated": 1772892827
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac3b2600000000004fd179",
      "text": " >ただ栄養補給のみを目的とした味気ない食事 [. https://wikiwiki.jp/singularity/頻出ミーム]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772895015,
      "updated": 1772895147
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac38d600000000004fd169",
      "text": " 自炊で本格的な料理せずに食材を焼いただけ、茹でただけ、レンチンしただけで食べてるときにこれになる",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772894422,
      "updated": 1772894643
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac388a00000000004fd15e",
      "text": " [ディストピア飯]で錠剤やペーストから栄養摂取するときにこれになる",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772894347,
      "updated": 1772894697
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac3ae100000000004fd177",
      "text": "  >[https://scrapbox.io/files/69ac3bd2f1c53c173228f34d.webp]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772894946,
      "updated": 1772895188
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac3bd900000000006a8130",
      "text": "   [エヴァンゲリオン]の映像みたい？",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772895194,
      "updated": 1772895208
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac387d00000000004fd15c",
      "text": "  > [https://gyazo.com/52c073fe31c97e2af5df4a60ef2ac9e6]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772894333,
      "updated": 1772895194
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac38f700000000004fd16a",
      "text": "   これは[2001年宇宙の旅]で宇宙船のクルーが食事をしている様子",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772894455,
      "updated": 1772894471
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac390700000000004fd16b",
      "text": "   ペースト状の何かを食べてる",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772894471,
      "updated": 1772894679
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac39d600000000004fd16d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772894679,
      "updated": 1772894716
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac39fa00000000004fd16e",
      "text": "食材を焼いただけ、茹でただけ、レンチンしただけの自炊でこれになる",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772894715,
      "updated": 1772894715
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac2f8a00000000004fd0de",
      "text": "　栄養はある",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772892042,
      "updated": 1772893459
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac325f00000000004fd11e",
      "text": "  野菜や肉魚豆など、気を使って栄養を摂る",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772892768,
      "updated": 1772893215
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac324b00000000004fd11a",
      "text": " 料理名がない",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772892747,
      "updated": 1772892838
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac31af00000000004fd112",
      "text": "  料理本/レシピサイトで取り上げられるような名前付きの料理でない",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772892592,
      "updated": 1772892617
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac32d500000000004fd120",
      "text": "   ハンバーグとか、生姜焼きとか、ほうれん草の胡麻和え……みたいな料理名がついてる食事をしない",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772892885,
      "updated": 1772893266
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac32bd00000000004fd11f",
      "text": "  フライパンで焼いたもの、レンチンしたもの、具沢山の味噌汁、それを毎日食べる",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772892861,
      "updated": 1772892906
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac32ea00000000004fd126",
      "text": "   文化的でない",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772892906,
      "updated": 1772892909
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac32db00000000004fd125",
      "text": "  火を通せば食べられる",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772892891,
      "updated": 1772892891
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac356600000000004fd13a",
      "text": "   レンチンしたスープとか",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772893542,
      "updated": 1772893561
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac33dd00000000004fd130",
      "text": " 食事の準備に時間を使いたくない",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772893149,
      "updated": 1772893149
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac2f1300000000004fd0cc",
      "text": "  食べないと健康でいられないから食べるけれど",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772891923,
      "updated": 1772893151
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac331200000000004fd127",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772892947,
      "updated": 1772892947
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac346e00000000004fd131",
      "text": "レンジでチンしただけの豚肉に塩胡椒をかけて食べる",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772893295,
      "updated": 1772893400
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac34cb00000000004fd135",
      "text": " 美味しい",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772893388,
      "updated": 1772893389
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac348900000000004fd133",
      "text": " 一緒に加熱した野菜と、別で温めておいたタッパーのご飯で食べる",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772893324,
      "updated": 1772893416
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac357e00000000004fd13e",
      "text": "  温野菜だと言えなくもない",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772893566,
      "updated": 1772893676
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac35ec00000000004fd140",
      "text": "   こう言えば寒々しい感じがしないかも",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772893676,
      "updated": 1772893679
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac34a100000000004fd134",
      "text": " 自分で調理した名前付きの肉料理より美味しい気がする……",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772893346,
      "updated": 1772893518
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac34ef00000000004fd136",
      "text": " 焼肉のタレで食べるのも美味しい",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772893423,
      "updated": 1772893429
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac35ff00000000004fd141",
      "text": "  [ベル食品 成吉思汗たれ]が美味しい",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772893695,
      "updated": 1772893731
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac355000000000004fd139",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772893521,
      "updated": 1772893521
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac364000000000004fd145",
      "text": "[健康で非文化的な最低限度の食事]で文化する",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772893761,
      "updated": 1772893764
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac375800000000004fd153",
      "text": " 同じものを食べるのはきついので何かしらする",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772894041,
      "updated": 1772894054
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac364400000000004fd147",
      "text": " 味付けにこる",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772893764,
      "updated": 1772893770
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac364900000000004fd148",
      "text": "  スープの味を変える",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772893770,
      "updated": 1772893974
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac367100000000004fd14a",
      "text": "   [鶏ガラスープ]のもとを使う",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772893810,
      "updated": 1772894019
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac374300000000004fd14e",
      "text": "   [ダシダ]を入れる",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772894019,
      "updated": 1772894731
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac394f0000000000f29aec",
      "text": "   \tこれは[ダシダ]だろうか🤔[terang.icon]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1772894543,
      "updated": 1772894552
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac3a0c00000000004fd16f",
      "text": "   \tそうです！！[vlzs.icon]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772894732,
      "updated": 1772894740
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac3a0f00000000004fd170",
      "text": "   \t 間違って読んでいたことを今知りました",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772894736,
      "updated": 1772894758
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac3a6c00000000006a812e",
      "text": "   \t ありがとうございます",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772894828,
      "updated": 1772894833
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac3a7f000000000021bddc",
      "text": "   \t あるある(´▽`)[terang.icon]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1772894847,
      "updated": 1772894872
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac374600000000004fd14f",
      "text": "   キムチを入れる",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772894023,
      "updated": 1772894024
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac36ac00000000004fd14b",
      "text": "  レンチンした野菜/肉に味付けする",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772893869,
      "updated": 1772893970
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac36cf00000000004fd14c",
      "text": "   塩胡椒",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772893903,
      "updated": 1772894027
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac374900000000004fd150",
      "text": "   焼肉用に売られてるブレンドスパイス調味料",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772894025,
      "updated": 1772894030
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac374d00000000004fd151",
      "text": "   ポン酢",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772894030,
      "updated": 1772894032
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac375000000000004fd152",
      "text": "   ドレッシング",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772894032,
      "updated": 1772894037
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac371800000000004fd14d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772893976,
      "updated": 1772893976
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac335800000000004fd128",
      "text": "[健康で文化的な最低限度の生活]をもじった言い方",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772893017,
      "updated": 1772893083
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac339a00000000004fd12a",
      "text": " [健康で非文化的な食事]というページタイトルのほうがいいかも",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772893083,
      "updated": 1772893083
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac339a00000000004fd12b",
      "text": " 最低限度という文言はいる？",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772893083,
      "updated": 1772893083
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac339a00000000004fd12c",
      "text": "  食べているときに粗食だなぁと思うのでいる",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772893083,
      "updated": 1772895262
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac339b00000000004fd12d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772893084,
      "updated": 1772893084
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac2f0f00000000004fd0ca",
      "text": "[https://www.nicovideo.jp/watch/sm40208334 僕が１年間ほぼ毎日食べてる料理【時短料理】 - ニコニコ動画]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772891919,
      "updated": 1772892168
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac301600000000004fd0e8",
      "text": " 看護師音声合成キャラクター・[雨晴はう]さんが投稿した料理動画",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772892183,
      "updated": 1772893078
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac300800000000004fd0e4",
      "text": " 安価な食材（業務スーパーの鶏胸肉、冷凍ブロッコリー、冷凍玉ねぎ）をレンジでチンして食べてる",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772892169,
      "updated": 1772892588
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac301300000000004fd0e6",
      "text": " 栄養がある",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772892179,
      "updated": 1772892179
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac2f0600000000004fd0c9",
      "text": " トマトスープ美味しそう[vlzs.icon]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772891910,
      "updated": 1772892455
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac2ecb00000000004fd0c1",
      "text": "  私が目指したい健康で非文化的な食事の例として挙げたかったけれど素敵なので例にならないかも",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772891852,
      "updated": 1772893492
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac33a700000000004fd12e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772893096,
      "updated": 1772893096
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac342f0000000000a19607",
      "text": " 「[食事]」であることが大事なんだと思う。単に栄養を補給するだけなら、それは「エサ」だ。 [suto3.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772893231,
      "updated": 1772893352
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac34340000000000a19608",
      "text": "  [たし🦀][vlzs.icon]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772893237,
      "updated": 1772893476
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac378c00000000004fd155",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772894092,
      "updated": 1772894092
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac351c00000000004fd137",
      "text": "外食をしたときに美味しくてびっくりする",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772893469,
      "updated": 1772894094
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac37d100000000004fd15b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772894161,
      "updated": 1772894161
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac379000000000004fd157",
      "text": "誰かに作ってもらった料理を久しぶりに食べると感動する",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772894097,
      "updated": 1772894156
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac377900000000004fd154",
      "text": " [健康で非文化的な食事]をしていると、自分で気が付かない間に心がげっそりしてそう",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772894073,
      "updated": 1772894136
    }
  ]
}